## Troubleshooting

### Checking Pod Status

```bash
# For Helm deployments
oc get pods -l app.kubernetes.io/name=developer-hub

# For Operator deployments
oc get pods -l rhdh.redhat.com/app=backstage-my-rhdh
```

### Viewing Logs

```bash
# Get logs from the main container
oc logs -l app.kubernetes.io/name=backstage -c backstage-backend

# Follow logs in real-time
oc logs -f -l app.kubernetes.io/name=backstage -c backstage-backend
```

### Verifying ConfigMaps and Secrets

```bash
# List ConfigMaps
oc get configmaps | grep rhdh

# View ConfigMap content
oc get configmap my-rhdh-app-config -o yaml

# List Secrets
oc get secrets | grep rhdh
```

### Restarting the Deployment

```bash
# For Helm
oc rollout restart deployment/rhdh-developer-hub

# For Operator
oc rollout restart deployment/backstage-my-rhdh
```
